        1302.3,
        2838.0
      ],
      "confiance": 1.0
    },
    {
      "texte": "If you're super completionist do the same thing for the pre-Socratic fragments. You won't understand them in their original form and it's not really important to at this point. Just read these at first:",
      "texte_balise": "If you're super completionist do the same thing for the pre-Socratic fragments. You won't understand them in their original form and it's not really important to at this point. Just read these at first:",
