    {
      "texte": "They'll fit into the historical context you already know and make a lot more sense. Actual Pre-Socratic fragments are recommended after getting a bit used to philosophy so you can see why they're cool.",
      "texte_balise": "They'll fit into the historical context you already know and make a lot more sense. Actual Pre-Socratic fragments are recommended after getting a bit used to philosophy so you can see why they're cool.",
      "bbox": [
