      "texte": "good annotated/commentary versions of Euripides, Sophocles, Aeschylus (the three tragedians), same for Aristophanes (comedy).",
      "texte_balise": "good annotated/commentary versions of Euripides, Sophocles, Aeschylus (the three tragedians), same for Aristophanes (comedy).",
